Package: mcgf
Title: Markov Chain Gaussian Fields Simulation and Parameter 
    Estimation
Version: 0.0.0.1000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tianxia", "Jia", , "tianxia.jia@ucalgary.ca", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5430-5019"))
Description: A package to simulate samples of (Regime-Switching) Markov chain 
    Gaussian fields with covariance functions of the Gneiting class. It supports 
    parameter estimation by weighted least squared and maximum likelihood 
    estimation methods, and produces kriging forecasts and intervals.
